search directory is folder from where it will pick all files.
If we enter y for caption then it will pick filename as caption.
Folder name is only for searching purpose or view purpose.
It will for other user as well. replace MohitCloud with your id. It is the same when you are setting tglogin.
If you don't enter username it will save it to saved messages else it will send it to that user. (public group/public channel/specific user having username)
Reference: https://pypi.org/project/telegram-cloud/#description